Directed by Richard Shepard. Nisha Ganatra. Gwyneth Horder-Payton. Matt Shakman.

Daxton Bloomquist (Chippendale Dancer). Max Teboul (Chippendale Dancer). Michael Graceffa (Richie). Graham Selden (The DJ). Odette Tyler (Club Patron). Robin de Jesus (Ray). Adam Ray (Larry). Maximilian Acevedo (Chippendales Dancer). Jack Laufer (Lew). Cyrus Hobbi (Chippendales Dancer). Danny Axley (Chippendales Dancer). Mona Sishodia (Steve’s Mom). Nathan Prevost (Chippendales Dancer). Roland Rusinek (Bernie). Zach Chyz (Chippendales Dancer). Chuck Saculla (Chippendales Dancer). Jacob Buckenmyer (Chippendale Calendar Model). Devinn Harris (New York Chippendales Dancer). Ben Bigler (Audition Dancer). Todd Christian Hunter (Chippendales Dancer).
